pageProduct.name: Thompson's Vitamin D3 1000IU 240 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's Vitamin D3 helps develop, strengthen and maintain healthy bones and teeth. It helps support muscle strength and may assist with bone density. It also assists with Calcium absorption, which is important in preventing osteoporosis in later life and may help reduce the incidence of fractures. It also supports the health and function of the skeleton, may assist in maintaining a healthy pregnancy, supports a healthy immune system and helps maintain general wellbeing.

Size: 240caps

Oil-Free?: Yes

Shelf Life in Days: 1095

KEY FEATURES

• Helps develop, strengthen and maintain healthy bones and teeth.
• Assists with Calcium absorption which is important in preventing osteoporosis in later life and may help reduce the incidence of fractures.
• May assist in maintaining a healthy pregnancy.
• Supports a healthy immune system.
• Helps maintain general wellbeing.

Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional. Vitamins supplements should not replace a balanced diet.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each capsule contains: Cholecalciferol 25 mcg
equiv. Vitamin D3 1000 IU

Contains: Cholecalciferol 25 mcg
equiv. Vitamin D3 1000 IU

Directions

Adults- Take one capsule daily (with food), or as professionally prescribed.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 30°C in a dry place. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Storage Temperature: below 30°C

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
